o------------------------------------------------------------------------------------o
|                          I N S T A L L A T I O N                                   |
o------------------------------------------------------------------------------------o

  1) Put the 'cal3d.dll' file of the Cal3D character animation library into
     the 3D Studio MAX directory.
     
  2) Put the 'cal3d_max_exporter.dle' file into the 'plugins' directory of 3D
     Studio MAX.

  3) Optional single window export interface, based on the maxscript API
     zip 'cal3D - Export.mzp' msrun.ms mzp.run '#scripts/export_cal3D/'[a-z]*
     Drag and drop the file on a 3D Studio MAX viewport (see the 
     #scripts/export_cal3D/readme.txt file for more information)

  4) Maxscript API documentation: read maxscript-api-export.txt
o------------------------------------------------------------------------------------o
